    <description>Patients treated with surgery alone for uterine cervical neoplasms attending surveillance at Dept. of Obstetrics and Gynecology, Oncogynecological unit, Aarhus University Hospital from 01.01.14 From 01.01.15 patients will be recruited from Oncogynecologic units at Aalborg University Hospital and Rigshospitalet. Recruitment of patients from these institutions has not been successful and has been closed.
